  <brief_title>Study to Assess Outcomes in Women Undergoing Either Hysteroscopic Sterilization (Essure®) or Laparoscopic Tubal Sterilization</brief_title>
  <official_title>An Open-label, Non-randomized, Prospective Observational Cohort Study to Assess Post Procedural Outcomes in Two Cohorts of Women Who Chose to Undergo Either Hysteroscopic Sterilization (Essure®) or Laparoscopic Tubal Sterilization</official_title>
