  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Pain: The proportion of AEs of chronic lower abdominal and/or pelvic pain after insertion of Essure System compared to the proportion of AEs of chronic lower abdominal and/or pelvic pain proportion of AEs of chronic lower abdominal and/or pelvic pain</measure>
